<item>
            <title>[PIG-4133] Need to update the default $HCAT_HOME dir in the PIG script.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4133</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Looks like we need to update the default HCAT_HOME in /bin/Pig to /usr/lib/hive-hcatalog.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is what it has currently.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;snip&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
if [ &quot;$HCAT_HOME&quot; == &quot;&quot; ]; then&lt;br/&gt;
  if [ -d &quot;/usr/lib/hcatalog&quot; ]; then&lt;br/&gt;
    HCAT_HOME=/usr/lib/hcatalog&lt;br/&gt;
  else&lt;br/&gt;
    echo &quot;Please initialize HCAT_HOME&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
    exit -1&lt;br/&gt;
  fi&lt;br/&gt;
  fi&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/snip&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
